high_descs: Turn right and go to the head of the dining table.
Pick up the box of tissues.
Turn right and go to the blue recycling container in the corner.
Place the box of tissues in the blue recycling container.
Turn left and go to the foot of the table.
Pick up the box of tissues there.
Turn left and go across the room to the blue recycling container in the corner.
Place the box of tissues in the blue recycling container.
anns.task_desc: Place two boxes of tissues from the table into the blue recycling container.

high_descs: Go to the corner of the table in the center of the room.
Pick up the box of tissues.
Go to the recycle bin in the corner by the window.
Put the box of tissue in the bin.
Go back to the end of the table.
Pick up the box of tissue on the table.
Take the tissues to the recycle bin in the corner.
Put the box of tissue in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Put two boxes of tissues in the recycle bin.

high_descs: Turn right, hang a left at the end of the table and walk to side of the table on the left.
Pick up the box of tissues from the left corner of the table.
Turn around and hang a left at the wall to reach the blue container in the corner on the floor.
Put the box of tissues inside the blue container on the floor.
Turn left, cross the room, hang a left at the green chair and turn left to face the side of the table.
Pick up the box of tissues to the left of the newspaper on the table.
Turn left, hang a right around the end of the table and turn left at the wall to face the blue container on the floor.
Put the box of tissues inside the blue container on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Place two boxes of tissue in a container.
